{
  "title": "Freshly Crispy Algerian Serrano Ham Tagine",
  "description": "A citrusy and crispy post-workout Algerian dish featuring Serrano ham, this recipe is dairy-free-friendly and served in a scallop shell. It is perfect for a snack or light meal.",
  "cuisine": "Algerian",
  "diet": [
    "dairy-free",
